snippet.title: Fracctal Monster Trailer (P2E Monster Taming Game)
snippet.description: Fracctal Monsters is a monster-taming game on the Algorand Blockchain. Players raise small pets from birth through feeding, playing, training, and exploring with their pets. Monsters grow and evolve over time.
